# Trivy ignore rules for intentional DLP demo fixtures
#
# This project is a Data Loss Prevention (DLP) platform demo. Some files
# deliberately contain PII/secret-like patterns to serve as test data for the
# DLP scanner. These files are not real credentials and should not trigger CI
# failures. Suppress by file path via the workflow's skip-files input.
#
# Any real credentials must NEVER be committed — use GitHub Secrets / a secrets
# manager and load them at runtime.
